abstract.para: A dataset containing all occurrences available in GBIF matching the query: { "TaxonKey" : [ "is Cherax tenuimanus Smith, 1912" ] } The dataset includes records from the following constituent datasets. The full metadata for each constituent is also included in this archive: 10 records from International Barcode of Life project (iBOL) 159 records from Western Australian Museum provider for OZCAM 9 records from South Australian Museum Adelaide provider for OZCAM 4 records from Natural History Museum (London) Collection Specimens 1 records from AM: Freshwater Invertebrates (1900-2005) 2 records from INSDC Sequences 4 records from NMNH Material Samples (USNM) 3 records from Queensland Museum provider for OZCAM 2 records from Crustacean specimens of Bihoro Museum 2 records from Tasmanian Museum and Art Gallery provider for OZCAM-Arthropoda 9 records from Museums Victoria provider for OZCAM 3 records from Naturalis Biodiversity Center (NL) - Crustacea 31 records from Australian Museum provider for OZCAM 1 records from NMNH Extant Specimen Records (USNM, US) 2 records from Tasmanian Museum and Art Gallery provider for OZCAM
